    "Section 3 addresses MLOps techniques, their limitations and common concerns regarding their utilization.",
    "It starts by presenting the MLOps typical workflow, involved challenges and some usual software tools.",
    "Then, AI/ML cloud trends are debated, namely ML as a service, cloud versus local solutions and hybrid clouds, along with some expected future developments.",
